@startuml component_diagram_modules

title Module Dependency — Calculator CLI

package "src/" {

    component "__main__.py" as Main {
        [main()]
    }

    component "cli.py" as CLI {
        [run_calculator()]
        [prompt_for_operator()]
        [prompt_for_first_number()]
        [prompt_for_second_number()]
        [display_result_unary()]
        [display_result_binary()]
        [display_error()]
        [OPERATIONS dict]
    }

    component "calculator.py" as Calc {
        [Calculator]
    }

}

package "stdlib" {
    component "math" as Math {
        [sqrt, factorial, log10, log]
    }
}

Main --> CLI : imports run_calculator,\ndisplay_error
CLI --> Calc : imports Calculator
Calc --> Math : imports math

note bottom of Main
  Entry point.
  Catches ZeroDivisionError
  and Exception.
end note

note bottom of CLI
  Arity-aware dispatch via OPERATIONS dict.
  Validation loops for all user inputs.
  Re-raises exceptions to main().
end note

note bottom of Calc
  Stateless pure methods.
  Raises ValueError or ZeroDivisionError
  on invalid inputs.
end note

@enduml
